A Drawing and Animation framework for teaching programmatic logic in Scala

------- sample code ------

class HelloCanvas extends Canvas {
    
    // Define a shape
    val mouseCicrle = new Ellipse( 0,  0, 80, 80, 1f, Color.GREEN, true, Color.RED)
    
    // Add the shape to the canvas
    canvas += mouseCicrle
    
    // Make the shape move
    override def animate() = {
        mouseCicrle.moveTo(mouseX, mouseY)
    }
    
}

------- run the examples ------

To test the files run the following:

mkdir bin
scalac -d bin -sourcepath src src/*.scala
cd bin
scala -classpath bin examples/MyCanvas.scala
